data.description: This stunning home 3 Bed, 3 FULL bath home in Carson Oaks offers the perfect blend of coastal charm, comfort, and convenience. The enclosed front porch is about to become your new favorite place for R&R! Upon entering the front door, you'll be greeted by the open living, dining, & kitchen space. You'll notice an array of upgrades such as the lighting, paint & custom window shades! The main floor is also home to one generously sized bedroom, a full bathroom & laundry room. On the second level, you'll find a versatile loft space with custom cabinetry, topped with granite for additional storage. The main suite is airy and bright. The main bath is complete with a double vanity, a spacious shower, & large walk-in closet. The additional bedroom upstairs also offers a full bath, granite, & walk in closet! This house is perfect for hosting multiple guests. All bedrooms & the loft have upgraded with gorgeous luxury vinyl flooring! The exterior of this home was recently repainted and BOTH A/C units were replaced in 2020. Brick pavers were added to the side yard providing a nice walk way to the back. Entering this community is enough to make you fall in love as it is saturated in beautiful Spanish moss, massive oak trees, and crepe myrtles that flourish throughout the neighborhood offering a sense of elegance that you won't find anywhere else. Take full advantage of the community pool, relax by the TVs, or play a game of pickleball on those warm summer days! Enjoy the PRIVATE Water Park with boat storage, kayak racks, docks, and a boat launch with deep water access! After a long day on the water, bring your fish and utilize the cleaning station. You can also clean your boat right there at the wash station. This area is gated and equipped with security cameras to ensure the safety of your items. Lawn and landscaping maintenance is included in the HOA Fees. This home is located 2 miles from Sandestin and 1 mile to the closest beach access!
